	eatuser_id,
	username,
	password,
	user_status,
	email,
	full_name,
	biz_name,
	mobile,
	nric,
	user_group,
	signup_date,
	company_dbname,
	active,
	bank_ac_no,
	bank_name,
	date_of_birth,
	entry_year,
	home_address,
	home_tel,
	agency,
	cut_to_agency,
	salesperson_share,
	apikey,
	agency_cea_reg,
	destination,
	agency_gst_reg
FROM
	eat_users
ORDER BY
	eatuser_id DESC
